{"key":"post-7768963","value":"<?xml version=\"1.0\"?>\n<post>\n<id>7768963</id>\n<content>The purpose of the 'roll' in dunk and roll is so that vermiculite will stick to the wet cake. Vermiculite absorbs water and therefore acts as a moisture reservoir.  You can mist the verm on the cake and it will slowly release that absorbed water to the mycelium.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Perlite does not absorb water.  Perlite is crystalline and is about as absorbant as window glass.  Putting perlite on your cakes will not serve as a moisture reservoir or anything else.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Read here: &lt;a href=&quot;/forums/showflat.php/Number/6610766#Post6610766&quot; class=&quot;pp&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://www.shroomery.org/forums/&lt;wbr&gt;showflat.php/Number/6610766#Post6&lt;wbr&gt;610766&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;RR</content>\n<name>RogerRabbit</name>\n<next>7769304</next>\n<prev>7768911</prev>\n<first>7767352</first>\n<last>7774029</last>\n<when>1197914687</when>\n<utime>12/17/07 08:04 PM</utime>\n</post>"}